uint32_t vpsissCalCmplxIoCfg::enable

FALSE disables, otherwise indicates the instance to be used. Valid values are 1 and 2

uint32_t vpsissCalCmplxIoCfg::pwrAuto

Auto power control mode of complex IO. TRUE configures it to enable auto power mode (in which power switches to ON / OFF based on ULP / ULPM commands from the sensor. Always powered on otherwise
